            h1(style="margin-top: 0px;") What is a 311 Call?
            div 311 is a service provided by the City of Minneapolis by which renters can inform the city of issues with the residence they are renting.  If a renter has already alerted the landlord to an issue, but it is not being resolved, 311 may be able to help resolve the issue.   There are several categories into which these types of complaints fall, but a few examples are:
            br
