                li Animal Complaint
                li Abandoned Vehicle Reports
                li Graffiti Report
                li Housing Code Violations
                li Noise Complaints
                li Residential Conditions Complaint
                li Sidewalk Snow and Ice
                li Street Light Out
            span For more information about 311 in Minneapolis please visit the official government page: 
             a(href= 'http://www.ci.minneapolis.mn.us/311/index.htm') http://www.ci.minneapolis.mn.us/311/index.htm
